<h1 style="margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 22px; color: #333;">Your Verification Code</h1>

<p style="font-size: 15px; color: #555; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  Use the code below to verify your email address.
</p>

<div style="text-align: center; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  <div style="display: inline-block; letter-spacing: 8px; font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #333; padding: 16px 24px; background-color: #f5f5f5; border: 1px solid #e0e0e0; border-radius: 8px;">
    <%= @code %>
  </div>
</div>

<div style="background-color: #fff8e1; border-left: 4px solid #fbc02d; padding: 14px 18px; border-radius: 4px; margin: 0 0 20px;">
  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #555; line-height: 1.5;">
    This code will expire in <strong>10 minutes</strong>.
  </p>
</div>

<p style="font-size: 14px; color: #999; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0;">
  If you didn't request this code, you can safely ignore this email.
</p>
